display_long_description:
# UNLEASH THE ORDNANCE WITH A PINCH OF YOUR FINGERS
Deploy your holographic command console anywhere to manage your city's defenses and protect your citizens. Thwart enemy attacks with carefully timed retaliatory strikes!

[media]

# IMPROVE YOUR REFLEXES & MASTER THE ARSENAL
If you survive the immediate onslaught, you'll get a chance to rebuild your city or upgrade your arsenal from a selection of missiles, bombs, drones and lasers.

[media]

# COMPETE WITH FRIENDS ON THE LEADERBOARDS
As you keep on fighting, you'll encounter increasingly fierce opposition. Will you achieve eternal glory on the leaderboards, or will your city fall under siege? The fate of your citizens rests in your hands!

[media]

# DEFEND YOUR CITY FROM ANYWHERE & ON-THE-GO
The command console can be deployed anywhere. Whether you find yourself on the living room sofa, on the toilet, outside or anywhere else, you can always quickly jump into the fight!

[media]

**"A must-have for Quest"** - UploadVR 🎖️

**"Breathes new life into an old game"** - MIXED News 🎖️

**"Gets your adrenaline pumping"** - 6DOF Reviews 🎖️

**"I'm actually blown away"** - Bill Carlton (Arcade Gaming Legend) 🎖️

# KEY FEATURES
- Game Modes: Training, Practice and Arcade
- 6 Training Maps; 7 Practice Maps; 2 Arcade Maps with Leaderboards
- 8 Turret types, 5 Enemy types
- 15 Turret Contracts (i.e. bounties/mini-quests)
- Different color palettes, pause system, tabletop repositioning
- And more still in development...

Join our Discord to share your feedback on the development roadmap:
**notsuspicious.biz/discord**
